{"tid":410500,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[自己頒傑出導師獎比自己] 何君堯老婆=何君堯=譚順生","createTime":"2017-09-23T03:49:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-23T11:23:14.000Z","uid":54373,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b23a2b54dc2864627bd8a33a37eefe520498a5ff","tid":410500,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T03:49:24.000Z","msg":"教育中心設傑出導師獎 陳浩明頒獎畀自己 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170615/large/1497537300_600b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170615%2Flarge%2F1497537300_600b.jpg&h=57ec39ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 由立法會議員<span style=\"color: red;\">何君堯太太陳浩明開設的博科教育中心</span>於2011年設立，其網站資料指陳浩明是「資深英語教育專家」，曾教導的學生來自超過30間本地及國際學校，包括聖保羅男女中學丶拔萃男書院等，<span style=\"color: red;\">形容自己「桃李滿門」；中心設傑出導師年獎，得獎人是陳浩明本人。<br />\n</span><br />\n位於炮台山桂洪集團中心501單位的博科教育中心，門外貼有大量師生合照，並於當眼位置貼有一張「傑出導師年獎」，得獎者為Cecilia Chan，即陳浩明本人。博科主打英語課程，由幼兒英語拼音丶中小學英語文法及寫作，到中學文憑試英語操練課程等應有盡有，每周一至六均有課程，每班大約5至6人，每堂約250至450元。<br />\n<br />\n以「樂學英語」作招徠的博科，不時上載陳與學生的合照，以及學生作品等。除授課外，陳亦曾出版英語教學書籍，主持研討會及工作坊等。"},{"pid":"0a24aff7d422b9b80fb92853dd4958f03510b524","tid":410500,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T03:50:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0a93825179cecdc15e8fd0d8a63ed5b39f2d860","tid":410500,"uid":56453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T03:50:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dbb72258744086f29f28a6211f2f5421ce2a2c5","tid":410500,"uid":59898,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T03:51:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" cla